to say goodbye to you at all.

296
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,110
No matter what,

297
00:20:05,220 --> 00:20:06,610
I want to tell you

298
00:20:08,660 --> 00:20:10,520
that you've always been my pride.

299
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:13,200
You've been independent and warm-hearted

300
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,460
since you were little.

301
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:15,700
That's just like me.

302
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,640
You have your own ideas,

303
00:20:18,770 --> 00:20:19,970
and you're stubborn.

304
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:21,740
That's just like your mom.

305
00:20:23,050 --> 00:20:24,580
But with your personality,

306
00:20:25,270 --> 00:20:26,330
I'm always worried

307
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:28,040
you'll

308
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,560
take a wrong turn.

309
00:20:30,770 --> 00:20:32,370
But thinking about it now...

310
00:20:32,610 --> 00:20:33,670
Actually, it's not

311
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:35,720
