for you to be like this.

312
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:37,700
No matter when,

313
00:20:39,020 --> 00:20:40,050
just be yourself.

314
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:46,210
You are my daughter,

315
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:49,340
but more importantly, you are yourself.

316
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:52,430
You don't need
to be like everyone else at all.

317
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:54,780
I know.

318
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:58,400
You always wanted me to have a stable

319
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:00,700
and smooth life.

320
00:21:01,460 --> 00:21:02,790
I have been trying hard.

321
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,400
I wanted to be that piece of the puzzle.

322
00:21:06,850 --> 00:21:08,980
But I was losing control more and more.

323
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:11,050
I couldn't control my time

324
00:21:11,430 --> 00:21:13,300
or my life.

325
00:21:14,550 --> 00:21:17,010
