347
00:22:55,290 --> 00:22:57,350
Our account has gone viral recently.

348
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,330
So many likes?

349
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:00,380
No wonder

350
00:23:00,380 --> 00:23:02,440
two more booking orders just came in.

351
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:06,160
I just got back.

352
00:23:06,190 --> 00:23:07,520
Why did you call me here?

353
00:23:07,750 --> 00:23:10,080
I still have a bunch
of deliveries to make.

354
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:13,920
The cleaning lady had something come up

355
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,000
and can't make it today.

356
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,290
It's just one room upstairs—

357
00:23:16,290 --> 00:23:17,250
the "Cinematic Memories" room.

358
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:18,580
Can you help me clean it?

359
