371
00:24:42,040 --> 00:24:45,660
♪ Thank you for your generosity ♪

372
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:50,390
♪ For making me believe in love ♪

373
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:05,220
You put it on?

374
