♪ When liberation comes ♪

446
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:23,590
♪ It is our sacred duty ♪

447
00:29:23,610 --> 00:29:29,970
♪ When liberation comes ♪

448
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:48,330
Laili.

449
00:29:50,350 --> 00:29:50,930
How is it?

450
00:29:51,590 --> 00:29:53,420
Does it feel familiar?

451
00:29:53,990 --> 00:29:55,230
I didn't expect

452
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:57,850
you to decorate this place like this.

453
00:29:58,530 --> 00:29:59,370
Do you like it?

454
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,510
I really love it.

455
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:03,970
Scoop out a big round piece,

456
00:30:03,990 --> 00:30:05,850
just like we did when we were kids.

457
00:30:06,990 --> 00:30:07,690
I thought

458
00:30:08,810 --> 00:30:10,590
that after this place was renovated,

459
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:12,050
our secret base from childhood

460
00:30:12,050 --> 00:30:12,930
would no longer exist.

461
00:30:12,930 --> 00:30:13,580
How could that be?

462
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:14,950
Exactly, how could that be?

463
00:30:14,950 --> 00:30:17,190
Guess which girl I saw Sadiq with

464
00:30:17,210 --> 00:30:19,310
at the cinema last week?

465
00:30:19,530 --> 00:30:21,120
What's there to guess?

466
00:30:21,150 --> 00:30:22,310
It was Gulistan.

467
00:30:22,340 --> 00:30:23,580
How do you know?

468
00:30:24,740 --> 00:30:26,390
He's single now.

469
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:28,880
He can watch movies with whoever he wants.

470
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,600
You are so open-minded.

471
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:31,140
Yeah.

472
00:30:32,850 --> 00:30:33,740
Actually,

473
00:30:34,020 --> 00:30:35,880
I thought about it for a long time.

474
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:37,850
It was not that he didn't love me.

475
00:30:37,850 --> 00:30:38,640
It was just

476
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:40,850
that the way he loved me
wasn't what I wanted.

477
00:30:40,850 --> 00:30:42,240
Then before...

478
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:45,240
It was my own choice
to marry someone I didn't love.

479
00:30:46,040 --> 00:30:48,770
But you had the courage
to bear everything after,

480
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:49,800
