484
00:31:07,170 --> 00:31:08,370
and reached out to me.

485
00:31:08,770 --> 00:31:09,980
That's a good thing.

486
00:31:12,990 --> 00:31:13,880
Then...

487
00:31:14,850 --> 00:31:16,720
Are you leaving again?

488
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:20,310
Honestly, my time back here

489
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:22,760
has been like a robot vacuum

490
00:31:23,170 --> 00:31:25,100
returning to its docking station:

491
00:31:25,470 --> 00:31:26,690
emptying the trash

492
00:31:26,800 --> 00:31:28,460
and getting fully recharged.

493
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,010
I can set off again.

494
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,870
Does Zhou Hengzhi know?

495
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:39,900
Whether he supports you or not,

496
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:41,140
we definitely support you.

497
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:42,400
Support you forever.

498
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,380
You're my backup.

499
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:48,770
No one is allowed to run away.

500
00:31:48,770 --> 00:31:49,710
You have to be here,

501
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:51,240
and you have to be here, too.

502
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:56,750
Hey Minawar,
I really want to see you dance.

503
00:31:56,850 --> 00:31:57,980
I want to see it, too.

504
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:00,180
Are you ready?

505
00:32:00,870 --> 00:32:02,180
Okay, let's start.

506
00:32:03,770 --> 00:32:05,530
3, 2, 1.

507
00:33:14,650 --> 00:33:15,810
You startled me.

508
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:17,370
That was the point.

509
00:33:18,500 --> 00:33:21,200
What are you doing here?

510
00:33:22,620 --> 00:33:23,140
Don't you go surprising me

511
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:25,540
