516
00:33:37,030 --> 00:33:38,290
You scared me to death.

517
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:39,320
But

518
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,020
I have a gift for you.

519
00:33:41,580 --> 00:33:42,340
Check it out.

520
00:33:53,380 --> 00:33:54,600
I know you want to go.

521
00:33:55,930 --> 00:33:58,170
It will be a bigger stage.

522
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,280
You can

523
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:02,170
