524
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,630
And this place and I

525
00:34:04,870 --> 00:34:06,270
shouldn't hold you back.

526
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:12,340
It's not that urgent.

527
00:34:13,310 --> 00:34:16,270
I'll go after everything is settled here.

528
00:34:17,420 --> 00:34:18,960
Who are you looking down on?

529
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:21,719
I'm the most professional
when it comes to homestays.

530
00:34:21,719 --> 00:34:22,510
Besides,

531
00:34:23,719 --> 00:34:25,550
